<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3586701>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. 1–3. Destinoides hainanensis sp. nov. Holotype: 1. habitus, dorsal view; 2. habitus, lateral view; 3. face; 4–6. Destinoides rubeus sp. nov. Holotype: 4. habitus, dorsal view; 5. habitus, lateral view; 6. face; Scale bars = 1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3586701/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3586703>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–13. Destinoides hainanensis sp. nov. 7. aedeagus, ventral view; 8. aedeagus, style and connective, lateral view; 9. connective, dorsal view; 10. pygofer side, lateral view; 11. subgenital plate, ventral view; 12. anal tube, lateral view; 13. male 8th sternite, ventral view. Scale bars = 1.0mm (Figs. 7–8, 10–13); 0.4mm (Fig. 9)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3586703/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3586705>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14–20. Destinoides rubeus sp. nov. 14. aedeagus, ventral view; 15. aedeagus, style and connective, lateral view; 16. connective,dorsal view; 17. pygofer side, lateral view; 18. subgenital plate, ventral view; 19. anal tube, lateral view; 20. male 8th sternite, ventral view. Scale bars = 1.0mm (Figs. 14–15, 17–20); 0.4mm (Fig. 16)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3586705/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

